1.Create a jar file:	
	1. Select project structure —>artifacts —> “+” add —>jar —> from module and dependencies	
  	2. Select the main class you you want to create to jar		
	3. Check — include in project build —> ok	
	4. Click build project button (left of the run/debug configuration menu)	
		jar file saved under:  out/artifacts folder/{project name}/xxx.jar	
		
	5. Run: 	
		java -jar xxxx.jar		
	
		
		
2. Bundling external dependencies with jar file— see:		
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mr2mPu1tLhk   #7		
